{
  "video_id": "yTR4sAD_4qM",
  "title": "Chade-Meng Tan: Everyday compassion at Google",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 20259.0,
      "text": "So what does the happiest man in the world look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 22260.0,
      "text": "He certainly doesn&#39;t look like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "He looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "His name is Matthieu Ricard."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "So how do you get to be the happiest man in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "Well it turns out"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "there is a way to measure happiness in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "And you do that by measuring the relative activation"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "of the left prefrontal cortex in the fMRI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "versus the right prefrontal cortex."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "And Matthieu&#39;s happiness measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 49260.0,
      "text": "is off the charts."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s by far the happiest man"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "ever measured by science."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 58260.0,
      "text": "Which leads us to a question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "What was he thinking when he was being measured?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "Perhaps something very naughty."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "Actually, he was meditating"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "on compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73260.0,
      "text": "Matthieu&#39;s own experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "is that compassion is the happiest state ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "Reading about Matthieu"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "was one of the pivotal moments of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "My dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "is to create the conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "for world peace in my lifetime --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "and to do that"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "by creating the conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "for inner peace"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "and compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "on a global scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "And learning about Matthieu"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "gave me a new angle to look at my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "Matthieu&#39;s brain scan shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "that compassion is not a chore."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "Compassion is something that creates happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "Compassion is fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 116260.0,
      "text": "And that mind-blowing insight"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "changes the entire game."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "Because if compassion was a chore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "nobody&#39;s going to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "except maybe the Dalai Lama or something."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "But if compassion was fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "everybody&#39;s going to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "Therefore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "to create the conditions for global compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "all we have to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "is to reframe compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "as something that is fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "But fun is not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "What if compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "is also profitable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 156260.0,
      "text": "What if compassion is also good for business?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "Then, every boss, every manager in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "will want to have compassion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "That would create the conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "for world peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "So, I started paying attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "to what compassion looks like in a business setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 177260.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, I didn&#39;t have to look very far."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 177260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "Because what I was looking for was right in front of my eyes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "in Google, my company."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "I know there are other compassionate companies in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "but Google is the place I&#39;m familiar with"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;ve been there for 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;ll use Google as the case study."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "Google is a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "born of idealism."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a company that thrives on idealism."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "And maybe because of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "compassion is organic"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "and widespread company-wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "In Google, expressions of corporate compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "almost always follow the same pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s sort of a funny pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "It starts with a small group of Googlers"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "taking the initiative to do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t usually ask for permission;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 226260.0,
      "text": "they just go ahead and do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 226260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "and then other Googlers join in, and it just gets bigger and bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "And sometimes it gets big enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "to become official."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "So in other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "it almost always starts from the bottom up."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240260.0,
      "text": "And let me give you some examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 240260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "The first example is the largest annual community event --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "where Googlers from around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "donate their labor to their local communities --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "was initiated and organized"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "by three employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "before it became official,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "because it just became too big."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "Another example, three Googlers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "a chef, an engineer"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "and, most funny, a massage therapist --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 268260.0,
      "text": "three of them, they learned about a region in India"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 268260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "where 200,000 people live"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "without a single medical facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 274260.0,
      "text": "So what do they do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 274260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "They just go ahead and start a fundraiser."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "And they raise enough money to build this hospital --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 282260.0,
      "text": "the first hospital of its kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 282260.0,
      "end_time": 284260.0,
      "text": "for 200,000 people."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 284260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "During the Haiti earthquake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 289260.0,
      "text": "a number of engineers and product managers"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 289260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "spontaneously came together"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "and stayed overnight"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "to build a tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "to allow earthquake victims to find their loved ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "And expressions of compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "are also found in our international offices."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "In China for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "one mid-level employee"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "initiated the largest social action competition in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "involving more than 1,000 schools in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "working on issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "such as education, poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "health care and the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "There is so much organic social action"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "all around Google"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "that the company decided to form"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "a social responsibility team"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "just to support these efforts."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "And this idea, again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "came from the grassroots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "from two Googlers who wrote their own job descriptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "and volunteered themselves for the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "And I found it fascinating"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "that the social responsibility team"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "was not formed as part of some grand corporate strategy."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "It was two persons saying, \"Let&#39;s do this,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "and the company said, \"Yes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 357260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "So it turns out"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "that Google is a compassionate company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "because Googlers found"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "compassion to be fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "But again, fun is not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "There are also real business benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "So what are they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 378260.0,
      "text": "The first benefit of compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 378260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "is that it creates highly effective business leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "There are three components of compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "There is the affective component,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392260.0,
      "text": "which is, \"I feel for you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 392260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "There is the cognitive component,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "which is, \"I understand you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "And there is a motivational component,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "which is, \"I want to help you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "So what has this got to do with business leadership?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "According to a very comprehensive study"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "led by Jim Collins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "and documented in the book \"Good to Great,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "it takes a very special kind of leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 418260.0,
      "text": "to bring a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 418260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "from goodness to greatness."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "And he calls them \"Level 5 leaders.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "These are leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "who, in addition to being highly capable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 432260.0,
      "text": "possess two important qualities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 432260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "and they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "humility and ambition."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "These are leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 442260.0,
      "text": "who are highly ambitious for the greater good."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 442260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "And because they&#39;re ambitious for a greater good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 447260.0,
      "text": "they feel no need to inflate their own egos."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 447260.0,
      "end_time": 449260.0,
      "text": "And they, according to the research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 449260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "make the best business leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 453260.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "And if you look at these qualities"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "in the context of compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "we find"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "that the cognitive and affective components of compassion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "understanding people and empathizing with people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "inhibits, tones down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 474260.0,
      "text": "what I call the excessive self-obsession that&#39;s in us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 474260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "therefore creating the conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 476260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "for humility."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "The motivational component of compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "creates ambition for greater good."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 485260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "In other words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "compassion is the way to grow Level 5 leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "And this is the first compelling business benefit."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "The second compelling benefit of compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 501260.0,
      "text": "is that it creates an inspiring workforce."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "Employees mutually inspire each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "towards greater good."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "It creates a vibrant, energetic community"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "where people admire and respect each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 512260.0,
      "end_time": 514260.0,
      "text": "I mean, you come to work in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 516260.0,
      "text": "and you work with three guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 516260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "who just up and decide to build a hospital in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like how can you not be inspired by those people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 526260.0,
      "text": "your own coworkers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 526260.0,
      "end_time": 528260.0,
      "text": "So this mutual inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 528260.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "promotes collaboration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 530260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "initiative and creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "It makes us a highly effective company."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "So, having said all that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 540260.0,
      "text": "what is the secret formula"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 540260.0,
      "end_time": 543260.0,
      "text": "for brewing compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 543260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "in the corporate setting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 547260.0,
      "text": "In our experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 547260.0,
      "end_time": 549260.0,
      "text": "there are three ingredients."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 551260.0,
      "text": "The first ingredient"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 551260.0,
      "end_time": 554260.0,
      "text": "is to create a culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 554260.0,
      "end_time": 556260.0,
      "text": "of passionate concern"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 556260.0,
      "end_time": 558260.0,
      "text": "for the greater good."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 558260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "So always think:"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "how is your company and your job"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "serving the greater good?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "Or, how can you further serve"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 569260.0,
      "text": "the greater good?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 569260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "This awareness of serving the greater good"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "is very self-inspiring"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 576260.0,
      "text": "and it creates fertile ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 576260.0,
      "end_time": 578260.0,
      "text": "for compassion to grow in."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 578260.0,
      "end_time": 580260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s one."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 580260.0,
      "end_time": 582260.0,
      "text": "The second ingredient"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 582260.0,
      "end_time": 584260.0,
      "text": "is autonomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 584260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "So in Google, there&#39;s a lot of autonomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "And one of our most popular managers jokes that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "this is what he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "\"Google is a place"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 596260.0,
      "text": "where the inmates run the asylum.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 596260.0,
      "end_time": 599260.0,
      "text": "And he considers himself one of the inmates."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 599260.0,
      "end_time": 601260.0,
      "text": "If you already have"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 601260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "a culture of compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 605260.0,
      "text": "and idealism"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 607260.0,
      "text": "and you let your people roam free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 607260.0,
      "end_time": 609260.0,
      "text": "they will do the right thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 609260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "in the most compassionate way."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "The third ingredient"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 617260.0,
      "text": "is to focus on inner development"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 619260.0,
      "text": "and personal growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 622260.0,
      "text": "Leadership training in Google, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 622260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "places a lot of emphasis on the inner qualities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "such as self-awareness, self-mastery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 631260.0,
      "text": "empathy and compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 631260.0,
      "end_time": 633260.0,
      "text": "because we believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 633260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "that leadership begins"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 638260.0,
      "text": "with character."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 638260.0,
      "end_time": 640260.0,
      "text": "We even created a seven-week curriculum"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 640260.0,
      "end_time": 642260.0,
      "text": "on emotion intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 642260.0,
      "end_time": 646260.0,
      "text": "which we jokingly call \"Searching Inside Yourself.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 646260.0,
      "end_time": 649260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s less naughty than it sounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 650260.0,
      "end_time": 652260.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m an engineer by training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 652260.0,
      "end_time": 656260.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m one of the creators and instructors of this course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 656260.0,
      "end_time": 658260.0,
      "text": "which I find kind of funny,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 658260.0,
      "end_time": 660260.0,
      "text": "because this is a company that trusts an engineer"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 660260.0,
      "end_time": 662260.0,
      "text": "to teach emotion intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 662260.0,
      "end_time": 664260.0,
      "text": "What a company."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 664260.0,
      "end_time": 666260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 669260.0,
      "text": "So \"Search Inside Yourself\" -- how does it work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 669260.0,
      "end_time": 671260.0,
      "text": "It works in three steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 671260.0,
      "end_time": 673260.0,
      "text": "The first step"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 673260.0,
      "end_time": 675260.0,
      "text": "is attention training."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 675260.0,
      "end_time": 678260.0,
      "text": "Attention is the basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 678260.0,
      "end_time": 683260.0,
      "text": "of all higher cognitive and emotional abilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 684260.0,
      "end_time": 686260.0,
      "text": "Therefore, any curriculum"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 686260.0,
      "end_time": 688260.0,
      "text": "for training emotion intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 688260.0,
      "end_time": 692260.0,
      "text": "has to begin with attention training."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 692260.0,
      "end_time": 695260.0,
      "text": "The idea here is to train attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 695260.0,
      "end_time": 697260.0,
      "text": "to create a quality of mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 697260.0,
      "end_time": 699260.0,
      "text": "that is calm and clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 699260.0,
      "end_time": 702260.0,
      "text": "at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 702260.0,
      "end_time": 704260.0,
      "text": "And this creates the foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 704260.0,
      "end_time": 707260.0,
      "text": "for emotion intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 707260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "The second step follows the first step."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 713260.0,
      "text": "The second step is developing self-knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 713260.0,
      "end_time": 715260.0,
      "text": "and self-mastery."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 715260.0,
      "end_time": 719260.0,
      "text": "So using the supercharged attention from step one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 719260.0,
      "end_time": 722260.0,
      "text": "we create a high-resolution perception"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 722260.0,
      "end_time": 725260.0,
      "text": "into the cognitive and emotive processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 725260.0,
      "end_time": 727260.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 727260.0,
      "end_time": 731260.0,
      "text": "It means being able to observe our thought stream"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 731260.0,
      "end_time": 733260.0,
      "text": "and the process of emotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 733260.0,
      "end_time": 735260.0,
      "text": "with high clarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 735260.0,
      "end_time": 737260.0,
      "text": "objectivity"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 737260.0,
      "end_time": 740260.0,
      "text": "and from a third-person perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 740260.0,
      "end_time": 742260.0,
      "text": "And once you can do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 742260.0,
      "end_time": 744260.0,
      "text": "you create the kind of self-knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 744260.0,
      "end_time": 747260.0,
      "text": "that enables self-mastery."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 748260.0,
      "end_time": 751260.0,
      "text": "The third step, following the second step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 751260.0,
      "end_time": 753260.0,
      "text": "is to create new mental habits."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 753260.0,
      "end_time": 756260.0,
      "text": "What does that mean? Imagine this."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 756260.0,
      "end_time": 759260.0,
      "text": "Imagine whenever you meet any other person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 759260.0,
      "end_time": 761260.0,
      "text": "any time you meet a person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 761260.0,
      "end_time": 764260.0,
      "text": "your habitual, instinctive first thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 764260.0,
      "end_time": 766260.0,
      "text": "is, \"I want you to be happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 766260.0,
      "end_time": 768260.0,
      "text": "I want you to be happy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 768260.0,
      "end_time": 770260.0,
      "text": "Imagine you can do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 770260.0,
      "end_time": 772260.0,
      "text": "Having this habit, this mental habit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 772260.0,
      "end_time": 775260.0,
      "text": "changes everything at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 775260.0,
      "end_time": 777260.0,
      "text": "Because this good will"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 777260.0,
      "end_time": 780260.0,
      "text": "is unconsciously picked up by other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 780260.0,
      "end_time": 783260.0,
      "text": "and it creates trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 783260.0,
      "end_time": 786260.0,
      "text": "and trust creates a lot of good working relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 787260.0,
      "end_time": 789260.0,
      "text": "And this also creates the conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 789260.0,
      "end_time": 792260.0,
      "text": "for compassion in the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 792260.0,
      "end_time": 795260.0,
      "text": "Someday, we hope to open-source"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 795260.0,
      "end_time": 797260.0,
      "text": "\"Search Inside Yourself\""
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 797260.0,
      "end_time": 800260.0,
      "text": "so that everybody in the corporate world"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 800260.0,
      "end_time": 803260.0,
      "text": "will at least be able to use it as a reference."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 804260.0,
      "end_time": 806260.0,
      "text": "And in closing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 806260.0,
      "end_time": 808260.0,
      "text": "I want to end the same place I started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 808260.0,
      "end_time": 810260.0,
      "text": "with happiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 810260.0,
      "end_time": 814260.0,
      "text": "I want to quote this guy -- the guy in robes, not the other guy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 814260.0,
      "end_time": 816260.0,
      "text": "the Dalai Lama,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 816260.0,
      "end_time": 818260.0,
      "text": "who said, \"If you want others to be happy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 818260.0,
      "end_time": 820260.0,
      "text": "practice compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 820260.0,
      "end_time": 822260.0,
      "text": "If you want to be happy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 822260.0,
      "end_time": 824260.0,
      "text": "practice compassion.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 824260.0,
      "end_time": 826260.0,
      "text": "I found this to be true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 826260.0,
      "end_time": 828260.0,
      "text": "both on the individual level"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 828260.0,
      "end_time": 830260.0,
      "text": "and at a corporate level."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 830260.0,
      "end_time": 832260.0,
      "text": "And I hope that compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 832260.0,
      "end_time": 834260.0,
      "text": "will be both fun and profitable for you too."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 834260.0,
      "end_time": 836260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 836260.0,
      "end_time": 842260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}